1
00:00:00,750 --> 00:00:04,420
[Never Too Late]

2
00:00:06,230 --> 00:00:10,210
[Episode 6]

3
00:01:01,470 --> 00:01:04,270
Don't grab my quilt!

4
00:01:04,270 --> 00:01:06,600
You pervert! When did you sneak into my house?

5
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:09,479
- You even sneaked into my bed.
- Jiang Xile, there was no one at home last night.

6
00:01:09,479 --> 00:01:11,579
How would I know you would suddenly…

7
00:01:13,210 --> 00:01:16,900
Jiang Xile, you're dressed. You're acting as if you're not.

8
00:01:16,900 --> 00:01:18,760
Bro, I'm not wearing a bra.

9
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:22,820
Even if you are not wearing a bra, there's no need to shout so loudly. The neighbors can hear you.

10
00:01:22,820 --> 00:01:27,679
You don't have to be so calm. Although you are a doctor and you've seen…

11
00:01:27,679 --> 00:01:32,879
You had treated me, but the situation is different now.

12
00:01:32,879 --> 00:01:34,628
I'll go out first.

13
00:01:40,820 --> 00:01:46,139
Baobei, do you think Xile and Ding Ran will fight under the same roof?

14
00:01:46,139 --> 00:01:49,980
No, being alone together can enhance feelings.

15
00:01:49,980 --> 00:01:57,380
Right now, I wish I could trap them both on a deserted island and let them share hardships to increase their affection.

16
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:06,740
- You're sure they won't fight?
- They won't.

17
00:02:06,740 --> 00:02:12,400
When they both return, we'll be the happiest family of four.

18
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:16,260
Why do I always feel that something big is going to happen?

19
00:02:16,260 --> 00:02:18,539
Don't think too much.

20
00:02:18,539 --> 00:02:19,490
[Baby]

21
00:02:21,212 --> 00:02:22,539
Hello, Baby.

22
00:02:22,539 --> 00:02:27,280
Mom, why didn't you tell me that Ding Ran was living in our house?

23
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:32,180
Dad, why didn't you tell me sooner that Jiang Xile would be coming back to stay?

24
00:02:33,090 --> 00:02:35,260
That's Xile's own house.

25
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:37,620
How would I know when she wants to go back to stay there?

26
00:02:37,620 --> 00:02:42,040
Baby, don't be angry. Listen to me.

27
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:44,379
You should know why she came back, right?

28
00:02:44,379 --> 00:02:46,679
Xiao Ran went back. He can just stay in our house.

29
00:02:46,679 --> 00:02:49,060
I heard your Auntie Baobei say that Xile had lost her job.

30
00:02:49,060 --> 00:02:52,200
She's in a bad mood. She went back to relax.

31
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:56,560
I warn you, be nice to Xile. Don't bully her anymore.

32
00:03:07,220 --> 00:03:09,140
Come and have breakfast.

33
00:03:17,030 --> 00:03:19,740
Why did my mom give you the key?

34
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:22,519
Your mom said that it was bad for the house to be unoccupied for a long time.

35
00:03:22,519 --> 00:03:25,700
I happened to be here, so I can look after it.

36
00:03:27,030 --> 00:03:32,560
When you came back last night, didn't you notice that someone was home?

37
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:36,519
I felt it was a bit strange, but I didn't think you would come back.

38
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:43,920
So, since you came, you've been staying in my room and sleeping in my bed?

39
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:49,739
Yes, but I changed to my own sheets and quilt cover. Don't worry.

40
00:04:06,020 --> 00:04:09,880
Why are you suddenly like a different person?

41
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:15,260
Now neither my dad nor your mom is here. We don't need to pretend to quarrel.

42
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:19,460
I'm not saying that we need to pretend to quarrel in front of our parents.

43
00:04:19,460 --> 00:04:24,280
I'm talking about the other day when you acted like you needed to draw a clear line with me.

44
00:04:25,620 --> 00:04:27,919
That was for another reason.

45
00:04:27,919 --> 00:04:30,099
What did you say?

46
00:04:30,099 --> 00:04:34,060
Well, our hospital and the town hospital are having an exchange program.

47
00:04:34,060 --> 00:04:38,260
I know that living with me in your current state must be very uncomfortable for you.

48
00:04:38,850 --> 00:04:42,179
I'll go to the hospital later to ask if there are other places where I can live.

49
00:04:42,179 --> 00:04:46,879
If I'm quick, I should be able to move out directly when I come back this evening.

50
00:04:46,879 --> 00:04:50,319
I didn't mean that you should move out immediately.

51
00:04:50,319 --> 00:04:51,980
I have to go to work now.

52
00:04:51,980 --> 00:04:53,759
You finish eating.

53
00:04:56,090 --> 00:04:59,000
Ding Ran. Ding Ran.

54
00:05:07,220 --> 00:05:12,060
Jiang Jiang, ask this lady for food from now on. Understand?

55
00:05:12,060 --> 00:05:14,519
Wait, it's name is Jiang Jiang?

56
00:05:14,519 --> 00:05:16,680
Are you cursing me?

57
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:19,920
- How did I curse you?
- I'm a dog, huh?

58
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:23,320
You're overthinking it. I just think it's quite cute, that's all.

59
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:26,899
Jiang Xile, quickly find me a pair of slippers.

60
00:05:26,899 --> 00:05:29,280
It's too hard to hail a cab here.

61
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:33,399
Find me a pair of slippers. My shoes stink from walking, smell it…

62
00:05:54,510 --> 00:05:56,900
Jiang Xile, I'm here.

63
00:05:57,700 --> 00:06:00,440
What a coincidence. Ding Ran is also here.

64
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:02,859
Lu Liuliu, what are you doing?

65
00:06:02,859 --> 00:06:05,279
NG, let's try it one more time?
(TN: NG abbreviated for no good)

66
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:15,179
As my old classmate, I hope you don't tell anyone about what just happened.

67
00:06:15,179 --> 00:06:16,379
Got it.

68
00:06:16,379 --> 00:06:18,219
Sensible.

69
00:06:18,820 --> 00:06:20,080
Can I leave now?

70
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:23,440
Of course. Let me open the door for you.

71
00:06:24,090 --> 00:06:27,799
Take care. Bye. Remember not to tell anyone.

72
00:06:27,799 --> 00:06:31,180
Stop shouting. He's not that bored.

73
00:06:33,030 --> 00:06:38,059
You have no idea how tired I am. Both tired and hot.

74
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:43,319
Why is Ding Ran here?

75
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:45,240
One room or two rooms?

76
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:48,020
- Did you sleep with him?
- How can we sleep together?

77
00:06:48,020 --> 00:06:49,160
You had tea?
(TN: a juicy scoop)

78
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:51,319
No.

79
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:58,940
Auntie Baobei, I saw Jiang Xile.

80
00:07:00,470 --> 00:07:03,000
Heartbroken and unemployed?

81
00:07:03,990 --> 00:07:06,160
She's not in a relationship with Zhang Ping'an?

82
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:08,260
She explicitly refused Xiao Zhang.

83
00:07:08,260 --> 00:07:10,780
She said she couldn't be with someone she didn't like.

84
00:07:10,780 --> 00:07:13,080
She said she didn't like Zhang Ping'an?

85
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:17,040
That's right. I hope you two can get along well.

86
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:20,260
Okay, Auntie Baobei, I will get along well with her.

87
00:07:20,260 --> 00:07:22,232
Keep it up.

88
00:07:22,232 --> 00:07:26,020
How can you suddenly seem like a different person?

89
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:32,220
It's too hot.

90
00:07:32,220 --> 00:07:35,039
Right, why is it so hot?

91
00:07:35,039 --> 00:07:36,960
Give me some wind.

92
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:39,699
- Feeling better?
- Yes.

93
00:07:39,699 --> 00:07:42,020
Why did you suddenly come to see me?

94
00:07:42,700 --> 00:07:44,860
Hide from Qi Fei.

95
00:07:44,860 --> 00:07:46,220
Promiscuous woman.

96
00:07:46,220 --> 00:07:49,879
He just wants to be in a relationship with you. Try it.

97
00:07:49,879 --> 00:07:53,160
He's such a kid. Does he know what it means to like someone?

98
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:54,860
It's just a whim.

99
00:07:54,860 --> 00:07:58,280
Maybe we won't see each other in the future.

100
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:03,040
You are usually extremely fashionable in the city, but now you're dressed like this.

101
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:06,840
Aren't you afraid that your old classmates will recognize you and runi your image?

102
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:09,000
Doesn't it look good? How fashionable.

103
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:11,200
Shiny, butterfly knot, isn't it fashionable?

104
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:13,120
If I wear it, it's fashionable.

105
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:18,020
Besides, at this time, except for you and me, no one else is idle enough to return to the village.

106
00:08:18,020 --> 00:08:20,220
That's right, it's so hot.

107
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:25,999
Why does that person look familiar?

108
00:08:27,110 --> 00:08:30,139
When did our village have such a striking young man?

109
00:08:30,139 --> 00:08:33,780
I didn't wear my contact lenses today. Is his face handsome?

110
00:08:33,780 --> 00:08:35,859
Seems okay.

111
00:08:36,460 --> 00:08:39,520
Take it. Let you see my strength.

112
00:08:49,030 --> 00:08:51,620
Handsome, are you looking for a homestay?

113
00:08:51,620 --> 00:08:55,299
I know a good homestay. Do you need me to recommend it to you?

114
00:08:55,299 --> 00:08:57,140
Liuliu.

115
00:09:01,010 --> 00:09:02,780
Qi Fei.

116
00:09:02,780 --> 00:09:05,280
Sorry, you've got the wrong person.

117
00:09:05,939 --> 00:09:08,239
Let's go, let's go.

118
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:12,700
You're Jiang Xile?

119
00:09:12,700 --> 00:09:14,279
Have some water.

120
00:09:14,279 --> 00:09:15,979
Thank you.

121
00:09:15,979 --> 00:09:17,920
By the way, where's Liuliu?

122
00:09:17,920 --> 00:09:22,959
Liuliu should be trying to salvage her image in your heart.

123
00:09:22,959 --> 00:09:26,200
She cares about her image in my heart?

124
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:28,500
She should.

125
00:09:28,500 --> 00:09:30,620
How did you know my full name?

126
00:09:30,620 --> 00:09:33,400
- I saw you in Ding Ran's old phone.
- Ding Ran's phone?

127
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:36,720
He always has your photos in his phone.

128
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:40,480
Jiang Xile, what time is it?

129
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:44,939
How come when I woke up from sleep, the sky is already dark?

130
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:49,759
You should wake up now. Look who's here.

131
00:09:51,839 --> 00:09:54,120
Qi Fei.

132
00:09:54,899 --> 00:09:57,400
How come you're here?

133
00:09:58,199 --> 00:10:00,579
When did you get here?

134
00:10:04,139 --> 00:10:07,719
Stop pretending, Lu Liuliu. I know it's you.

135
00:10:07,719 --> 00:10:11,740
The slippers under your feet are exactly the same.

136
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:22,640
Qi Fei. You are quite handsome,

137
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:26,680
but why are you a little bit persistent? You followed me here?

138
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:30,140
I didn't come following you. I came to see my friend.

139
00:10:30,140 --> 00:10:33,080
In this village, what friends can you have?

140
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:36,000
The greengrocer or the butcher?

141
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:38,340
Hello. Where are you?

142
00:10:38,340 --> 00:10:40,040
I'm back.

143
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:48,700
Why are there so many people?

144
00:10:48,700 --> 00:10:50,560
It was you who flirted with me at the beginning.

145
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:52,820
Why don't you want to acknowledge our relationship?

146
00:10:52,820 --> 00:10:56,740
I acknowledge it. But in the beginning, it was you who asked me if I wanted to have tea.

147
00:10:56,740 --> 00:10:59,899
I simply asked you whether you wanted to have tea.

148
00:10:59,899 --> 00:11:03,779
What does having tea mean? We're both adults. Who doesn't understand

149
00:11:03,779 --> 00:11:06,620
The meaning of having tea? Having tea is just having tea.

150
00:11:06,620 --> 00:11:08,480
Doesn't having tea mean that?

151
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:10,440
- How do you all know each other?
- What meaning does it have?

152
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:12,099
- What did I mean?
- Just that.

153
00:11:12,099 --> 00:11:16,000
I didn't expect that the person Qi Fei fell in love with at first sight was Lu Liuliu.

154
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,959
Really to have tea.

155
00:11:17,959 --> 00:11:20,280
Do you know what having tea means?

156
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:23,900
We don't... want to know.

157
00:11:23,900 --> 00:11:27,799
Isn't that what you meant? At least, when you were having tea, you were very happy.

158
00:11:27,799 --> 00:11:30,459
Weren't you happy? Was that happiness only mine?

159
00:11:30,459 --> 00:11:33,159
I was happy, but why do we have to be in a relationship?

160
00:11:33,159 --> 00:11:36,360
What do you mean by having to be in a relationship? We're both men. You ask Ding Ran,

161
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:39,060
isn't it happier to be in a relationship?

162
00:11:39,060 --> 00:11:40,219
I don't know.

163
00:11:40,219 --> 00:11:43,139
Ding Ran said he didn't know. That means it was not happy.

164
00:11:43,139 --> 00:11:47,099
- He is not in a relationship. How would he know?
- How many relationships have you had?

165
00:11:49,139 --> 00:11:50,879
Haven't had any.

166
00:11:52,160 --> 00:11:55,780
Jiang Xile, fortunately, you weren't in a relationship with Ding Ran back then.

167
00:11:55,780 --> 00:11:58,259
Why are you mentioning the past to me?

168
00:11:58,259 --> 00:12:00,560
What past? Have you forgotten?

169
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:04,439
Back then, when you were ready to confess to Ding Ran, Xu Shanshan suddenly caused trouble.

170
00:12:04,439 --> 00:12:09,920
- If you two were really in a relationship, Xu Shanshan would definitely find ways to mess with you.
- Lu Liuliu, stop

171
00:12:09,920 --> 00:12:13,060
What do you mean by Xu Shanshan causing trouble?

172
00:12:14,750 --> 00:12:18,310
[Happy Graduation from Xiangyang Middle School]

173
00:12:23,838 --> 00:12:27,227
[Ten Years Ago]

174
00:12:39,039 --> 00:12:40,979
Miss, did you see Jiang Xile?

175
00:12:40,979 --> 00:12:43,320
I just saw her in the classroom.

176
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:45,719
The classroom. Thank you.

177
00:12:53,079 --> 00:12:56,640
Jiang Xile, are you going to confess to Ding Ran?

178
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:59,799
Whether I want to confess to Ding Ran or not is none of your business.

179
00:12:59,799 --> 00:13:01,520
Do you dare to bet with me?

180
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:04,400
If your confession fails, you can never pester him again.

181
00:13:04,400 --> 00:13:07,360
Boring, who wants to bet with you?

182
00:13:08,259 --> 00:13:10,660
Ding Ran and I are both high-scoring students.

183
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:12,960
With our scores, we can easily get into medical school.

184
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:16,119
How much can you score? Can you get into university?

185
00:13:16,119 --> 00:13:18,300
Don't you feel ashamed to pester so much?

186
00:13:18,300 --> 00:13:19,780
What do I have to be ashamed of?

187
00:13:19,780 --> 00:13:22,839
Now that we're all graduating if I could date Ding Ran…

188
00:13:22,839 --> 00:13:24,239
If you could date Ding Ran, so what?

189
00:13:24,239 --> 00:13:28,179
If I could date Ding Ran, I could take away one thing you like.

190
00:13:28,179 --> 00:13:30,319
I'll piss you off. Let you target me again.

191
00:13:30,319 --> 00:13:32,999
Jiang Xile, you…

192
00:13:32,999 --> 00:13:34,460
What you?

193
00:13:34,460 --> 00:13:38,079
When my confession is successful, I'll notify you first.

194
00:13:59,594 --> 00:14:01,392
[Ding Ran Xile]

195
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:11,140
Did you know when Jiang Xile was coldly and cruelly refused by you,

196
00:14:11,140 --> 00:14:12,999
her tears wet her pillow that night?

197
00:14:12,999 --> 00:14:15,059
- I thought once—
- What the hell were you thinking?

198
00:14:15,059 --> 00:14:17,800
You didn't see Xu Shanshan's face.

199
00:14:17,800 --> 00:14:19,760
Jiang Xile.

200
00:14:19,760 --> 00:14:24,219
Jiang Xile, are you trying to piss me off?

201
00:14:26,660 --> 00:14:32,479
That night, you put the shirt Jiang Xile gave you on Xu Shanshan.

202
00:14:32,479 --> 00:14:34,380
Which girl can tolerate that?

203
00:14:34,380 --> 00:14:37,799
She insisted on taking that shirt from me.

204
00:14:39,019 --> 00:14:41,420
Why were you so careless?

205
00:14:43,880 --> 00:14:46,080
- What happened?
- Shanshan fell into the water.

206
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:48,859
Wait a minute, I'll get you a towel.

207
00:14:48,859 --> 00:14:55,600
♫ Page by page, the photos look more like full stops  ♫

208
00:14:56,220 --> 00:14:58,560
Ding Ran, I'm so cold.

209
00:14:58,560 --> 00:15:01,579
Can you lend me your shirt?

210
00:15:03,620 --> 00:15:04,720
Thanks.

211
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:07,880
She said she was very cold and then she took my shirt.

212
00:15:07,880 --> 00:15:10,700
Why did you care if she was cold?

213
00:15:10,700 --> 00:15:11,980
Right.

214
00:15:11,980 --> 00:15:14,859
Whether Xu Shanshan was cold or not was none of my business.

215
00:15:16,900 --> 00:15:19,790
Do you still like Jiang Xile now?

216
00:15:19,790 --> 00:15:22,070
♫ All these years, we cried and laughed are memories we cherished ♫

217
00:15:22,070 --> 00:15:26,739
I thought she was with that Zhang Ping'an.

218
00:15:26,739 --> 00:15:28,239
Don't go assuming again.

219
00:15:28,239 --> 00:15:31,139
Don't you have a mouth? Can't you ask?

220
00:15:31,139 --> 00:15:34,460
♫ A heart shattered in regrets is hard to mend ♫

221
00:15:34,460 --> 00:15:38,440
Ding Ran, I want to date you. What do you think?

222
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:41,240
I don't have time to participate in your boring life.

223
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:45,680
♫ My willingness to be cute is not simple ♫

224
00:15:45,680 --> 00:15:47,839
What a waste of a mouth.

225
00:15:51,474 --> 00:15:54,932
♫ We loved deeply in those years and learned to gracefully let go ♫

226
00:15:54,932 --> 00:15:59,307
♫ Feeling lost and alone in the crowd ♫

227
00:15:59,307 --> 00:16:05,239
♫ We eventually go our separate ways ♫

228
00:16:05,239 --> 00:16:08,460
- Have you packed up your belongings?
- Yes.

229
00:16:10,159 --> 00:16:12,920
Don't take Lu Liuliu's words to heart.

230
00:16:12,920 --> 00:16:17,180
After all, it's been so long. We're not high school students anymore.

231
00:16:17,180 --> 00:16:19,620
We're definitely not high school students anymore.

232
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:22,600
So, is the place you're moving to far away?

233
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:24,720
Not far, it's quite near.

234
00:16:24,720 --> 00:16:26,999
Just downstairs.

235
00:16:26,999 --> 00:16:29,480
That's not far.

236
00:16:32,999 --> 00:16:35,340
Aren't you moving out?

237
00:16:35,340 --> 00:16:39,560
Yes, moving downstairs. Your room is still yours.

238
00:16:39,560 --> 00:16:42,819
Didn't you say yesterday that you were going to move out?

239
00:16:42,819 --> 00:16:47,639
Ding Ran, where are you going to stay later? I'll go with you.

240
00:16:47,639 --> 00:16:50,620
I'm not going. Find a place yourself.

241
00:16:50,620 --> 00:16:53,940
By the way, I think Lu Liuliu is really good.

242
00:16:53,940 --> 00:16:56,420
It's worth trying for again.

243
00:16:57,760 --> 00:17:00,039
Help me put this in the room.

244
00:17:01,079 --> 00:17:04,280
Let's go. Let's talk alone.

245
00:17:05,079 --> 00:17:07,300
Where are you going?

246
00:17:17,299 --> 00:17:19,100
I want to talk to you about three things.

247
00:17:19,100 --> 00:17:22,720
What do you want to talk to me? It's stuffy and hot here.

248
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:25,620
First, I won't move out today.

249
00:17:25,620 --> 00:17:28,299
Second, I won't move out tomorrow, either.

250
00:17:28,299 --> 00:17:29,939
Third…

251
00:17:33,239 --> 00:17:35,200
What's the third?

252
00:17:36,520 --> 00:17:39,340
Third, your mom told me to get along with you.

253
00:17:39,340 --> 00:17:41,760
I think she's quite right.

254
00:17:45,879 --> 00:17:48,160
Now it's my turn to ask you.

255
00:17:50,279 --> 00:17:52,640
Is Zhang Ping'an your boyfriend?

256
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:56,560
There's nothing between Ping'an and me. We made that clear a long time ago.

257
00:17:56,560 --> 00:18:02,620
Although I was prepared, I didn't expect you to refuse me so directly.

258
00:18:03,819 --> 00:18:06,640
There was not even a word of praise for me.

259
00:18:06,640 --> 00:18:09,160
Right, Ping'an.

260
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:10,640
You are a good man.

261
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:15,319
You are the nicest and most upright guy I ever met after I started working.

262
00:18:15,319 --> 00:18:18,340
You're sincere, reliable, and excellent.

263
00:18:18,340 --> 00:18:21,160
You don't even curse when you're stuck in traffic.

264
00:18:22,360 --> 00:18:26,380
What are you laughing at? I'm seriously praising you.

265
00:18:26,380 --> 00:18:31,819
Every time I'm with you, I feel you're really great.

266
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:38,160
So, if in this lifetime, one could only fall in love and get married to one person,

267
00:18:38,160 --> 00:18:43,220
I think both you and I should find someone we like.

268
00:18:46,420 --> 00:18:51,720
I should give myself more chances to meet other people.

269
00:18:59,119 --> 00:19:02,420
Xile, can I hug you?

270
00:19:10,760 --> 00:19:14,880
In this way, Zhang Ping'an is really not bad.

271
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:17,400
What do you mean not bad? He's very good.

272
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:21,380
- Then he's worthy of a "Good Man Card."
- Don't misconstrue the definition of a good man.

273
00:19:23,039 --> 00:19:24,839
Forget it.

274
00:19:24,839 --> 00:19:28,999
Let's turn the page on this. You can stay if you want.

275
00:19:53,480 --> 00:19:55,260
Let me help you.

276
00:19:55,260 --> 00:19:59,199
- These are ready. Take them over first.
- All right.

277
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:03,300
I wonder what Liuliu and Qi Fei are doing.

278
00:20:03,300 --> 00:20:05,420
I'll call them to have dinner.

279
00:20:06,370 --> 00:20:07,460
[Wilted Flower Emoji]
(TN: slang for doing the deed)

280
00:20:08,900 --> 00:20:11,079
Ding Ran, wait a second.

281
00:20:13,720 --> 00:20:17,920
Lu Liuliu really is saying one thing and doing another.

282
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:20,339
They're not fighting again, are they?

283
00:20:20,339 --> 00:20:23,280
- I'll go take a look.
- No, no,

284
00:20:23,999 --> 00:20:27,099
you can't go up now.

285
00:20:42,959 --> 00:20:45,560
Weren't you trying to get rid of me?

286
00:20:45,560 --> 00:20:51,460
You just did something that I've always wanted to do since I was a girl.

287
00:20:51,460 --> 00:20:55,380
Having heard such words, whether male or female, how could he not feel a little unacceptable?

288
00:20:55,380 --> 00:20:57,420
Unacceptable?

289
00:20:57,420 --> 00:21:01,600
How good was Jiang Xile to him! Didn't he have eyes? Didn't he have a heart?

290
00:21:01,600 --> 00:21:05,199
If I hadn't cleared up what happened back then, would he never ask?

291
00:21:05,199 --> 00:21:09,520
I need to clarify it with her. I can't let her be fooled by Ding Ran.

292
00:21:09,520 --> 00:21:13,340
Liuliu, they can resolve their own issues.

293
00:21:13,340 --> 00:21:17,759
With their personalities, bickering, and dawdling, what problems can they solve?

294
00:21:17,759 --> 00:21:19,096
♫ I look like a hooligan ♫

295
00:21:19,096 --> 00:21:20,626
♫ But I'm warm and want to... ♫

296
00:21:20,626 --> 00:21:22,324
♫ Move into your heart immediately ♫

297
00:21:22,324 --> 00:21:23,480
♫ It's like I've caught a cold ♫

298
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:26,500
Lu Liuliu, they're not kids.

299
00:21:26,500 --> 00:21:29,839
They can resolve their own problems.

300
00:21:29,839 --> 00:21:35,099
Can we first resolve our own problems before meddling in others'?

301
00:21:37,340 --> 00:21:41,180
I've always thought you were a kid.

302
00:21:41,180 --> 00:21:45,220
Just now, suddenly, I felt you were a bit different.

303
00:21:45,220 --> 00:21:47,320
Where am I different?

304
00:21:49,114 --> 00:21:55,874
♫ Don't doubt the weight you carry in my heart  ♫

305
00:21:55,874 --> 00:21:58,519
♫ I'm a mess ♫

306
00:21:58,519 --> 00:22:01,100
♫ Love is poison ♫

307
00:22:01,100 --> 00:22:03,400
♫ What should I do? ♫

308
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:07,840
Do you treat everyone else like this?

309
00:22:07,840 --> 00:22:10,180
I only treat you like this.

310
00:22:11,670 --> 00:22:13,528
♫ I like your fragrance ♫

311
00:22:13,528 --> 00:22:16,234
♫ Let this love surround us ♫

312
00:22:16,234 --> 00:22:19,538
♫ My eyes are the recording device for you ♫

313
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:30,179
- Hello.
- Hello.

314
00:22:30,179 --> 00:22:33,380
Lu Liuliu, I'm getting married.

315
00:22:33,380 --> 00:22:36,980
Say, do you think anyone will want you in this lifetime?

316
00:22:45,500 --> 00:22:47,380
What's wrong?

317
00:22:48,059 --> 00:22:50,079
Nothing.

318
00:22:50,079 --> 00:22:55,580
Qi Fei, can you see if you can stay at Ding Ran's tonight?

319
00:22:55,580 --> 00:22:58,059
I want to be alone.

320
00:22:59,199 --> 00:23:01,560
What happened?

321
00:23:01,560 --> 00:23:04,179
My ex-boyfriend is getting married.

322
00:23:05,259 --> 00:23:07,900
You have an ex-boyfriend?

323
00:23:07,900 --> 00:23:10,199
Is an ex-boyfriend some kind of rare species?

324
00:23:10,199 --> 00:23:12,340
Can I not have one?

325
00:23:13,179 --> 00:23:15,600
Didn't you say you didn't date?

326
00:23:15,600 --> 00:23:17,280
I…

327
00:23:22,300 --> 00:23:25,619
Why is Ding Ran suddenly acting strange?

328
00:23:32,199 --> 00:23:34,619
What does he want to do?

329
00:23:42,440 --> 00:23:46,820
He's getting married, but I can't sleep.

330
00:23:51,420 --> 00:23:55,719
What exactly happened between her and her ex-boyfriend?

331
00:23:57,300 --> 00:24:01,600
Starting from tomorrow, will we have a new beginning?

332
00:24:02,762 --> 00:24:10,460
♫ Page by page, the photos look more like full stops  ♫

333
00:24:10,460 --> 00:24:17,944
♫ I'm alone in my room, reminiscing about the past ♫

334
00:24:17,944 --> 00:24:25,564
♫ No matter how far the lens of memory can reach, it will eventually lose focus ♫

335
00:24:25,564 --> 00:24:35,096
♫ It is a natural part of life for adults to come and go ♫

336
00:24:35,096 --> 00:24:41,236
♫ All these years, we cried and laughed are memories we cherished ♫

337
00:24:41,236 --> 00:24:46,499
♫ In a blink of an eye, time encourages change ♫

338
00:24:46,499 --> 00:24:50,328
♫ A heart shattered in regrets is hard to mend ♫

339
00:24:50,328 --> 00:24:54,712
♫ It may take several more years to forget those years ♫

340
00:24:54,712 --> 00:24:58,648
♫ My willingness to be cute is not simple ♫

341
00:24:58,648 --> 00:25:06,441
♫ My willingness to be cute is not simple ♫
